The 25th edition of the Kenya Homes Expo will open its doors to the public next Thursday at the Kenyatta International Convention Centre, Nairobi. The four-day event will run from April 27 to 30, showcasing products tailored for the low- and middle-income earners. East African Portland Cement Company, which has sponsored the expo for six straight years, is once again the title sponsor. Vaal Real Estate, a sales and marketing company that develops high-end homes will sponsor the expo for the first time.&nbsp;